WEBVTT

00:01.173 --> 00:03.663
(J) Um... Mom OD'd. She died.

00:03.687 --> 00:06.612
(Smurf) Sweetheart, why don't you
just go and pack up your things.

00:07.055 --> 00:08.681
You remember your uncles, don't you, J?

00:08.714 --> 00:09.914
- Hey.
- Hey.

00:09.939 --> 00:11.965
What makes you think that
we can trust this kid?

00:11.990 --> 00:14.534
The kid is in until I say he isn't.

00:14.559 --> 00:16.663
J, can you hear me? What hap...?

00:16.952 --> 00:18.714
You just ruined my surprise.

00:18.739 --> 00:20.494
(Pope) So, what are we planning next?

00:22.795 --> 00:25.064
J, she died?

00:25.865 --> 00:28.451
Just toss me a bone, man.
Smurf doesn't have to know.

00:28.476 --> 00:31.445
They need a car for the thing.

00:31.469 --> 00:34.247
- [Panting]
- (Baz) The car, Pope. Nothing else.

00:34.272 --> 00:36.308
You don't remember our
faces. I know where you live.

00:36.332 --> 00:37.830
DNA jackpot.

00:42.129 --> 00:43.918
(Craig) Uh, oh, shit!

00:46.894 --> 00:48.796
- [Gunshot, glass shatters]
- Whoa! Shit.

00:48.828 --> 00:51.599
[Indistinct shouting]

00:54.156 --> 00:55.724
Give this to your girl.

00:55.835 --> 00:58.238
Girls like shiny stuff.

01:01.001 --> 01:02.795
- Get back!
- (laughing)

01:03.133 --> 01:04.897
♪♪

01:04.923 --> 01:07.193
- Let it go!
- Pass it!

01:07.540 --> 01:09.728
- Oh!
- Go, J!

01:09.753 --> 01:12.322
[Cheering]

01:12.963 --> 01:14.632
Pass the ball, Pope!

01:14.922 --> 01:16.992
Oh! Here we go!

01:17.768 --> 01:19.403
Get it, Pope!

01:19.436 --> 01:21.338
Get him!

01:21.798 --> 01:23.299
Do it! Get in there!

01:24.387 --> 01:25.839
Man down!

01:27.000 --> 01:33.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:39.709 --> 01:41.815
- You all right?
- Little prick.

01:41.847 --> 01:43.764
- Yeah!
- You okay?

01:43.927 --> 01:45.894
You do that, you're gonna get hit.

01:46.779 --> 01:48.699
That's his way of saying sorry.

01:49.292 --> 01:52.296
♪♪

01:54.363 --> 01:55.798
Oh!

02:02.141 --> 02:04.601
Oh, Jesus. Not this shit again.

02:10.044 --> 02:12.033
Hey. Who are you rooting for, Ma?

02:12.058 --> 02:14.863
Both of them, baby. That's
the beauty of being a mother.

02:14.888 --> 02:16.707
You never have to pick sides.

02:27.301 --> 02:29.613
Come on, honey. Why don't you
help me with the food trays?

02:29.638 --> 02:30.842
Yeah, sure.

02:35.417 --> 02:36.680
You all right?

02:41.534 --> 02:42.737
Hey.

02:43.218 --> 02:44.693
I scored. You got to drink.

02:44.718 --> 02:46.093
(Baz) Give him a break, man.

02:46.118 --> 02:48.430
It's barely noon, and
the kid's already had six.

02:49.401 --> 02:51.036
Drink. It's the rules.

03:02.659 --> 03:03.859
[Coughs]

03:09.910 --> 03:11.684
God, do you always cook like this?

03:11.709 --> 03:13.827
My boys have big appetites.

03:14.974 --> 03:16.176
Here.

03:17.724 --> 03:20.745
If you were shipwrecked
on a desert island

03:20.770 --> 03:23.728
and you could only choose
one, who would you pick?

03:24.794 --> 03:26.737
Other than J, of course.

03:27.184 --> 03:29.939
Just asking. You're a
beautiful young girl.

03:33.181 --> 03:34.381
(scoffs)

03:35.150 --> 03:37.056
Baz is pretty cool.

03:37.945 --> 03:41.783
♪♪

03:41.992 --> 03:47.698
♪ She stares deeply ♪

03:47.732 --> 03:51.603
♪ Locked inside me ♪

03:51.635 --> 03:54.605
♪ Burnin' brightly ♪

03:57.641 --> 04:02.547
♪ One they know that I cannot take ♪

04:03.398 --> 04:06.984
♪ Waitin' for it all to begin ♪

04:07.018 --> 04:10.589
♪ Every night now, they'll win ♪

04:14.205 --> 04:16.454
♪ Come and meet my black hole ♪

04:16.478 --> 04:20.331
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

04:20.363 --> 04:24.480
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

04:24.505 --> 04:28.125
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

04:28.150 --> 04:32.320
♪ Got a big black, big black hole ♪

04:32.345 --> 04:34.337
♪ Got a big black hole ♪

04:34.362 --> 04:38.314
- ♪ Inside of me. Got a ♪
